《'''The Powder Toy'''》是一款“落沙物理沙盘”[[电脑游戏|电脑游戏]]，它可以模拟空气的[[压强|压强]]、[[流速|流速]]以及[[热量|热量]]<ref>{{cite web|title=The Powder Toy|url=http://powdertoy.co.uk/|accessdate=2012-03-27|language=en|archive-date=2012-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120406154220/http://powdertoy.co.uk/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，游戏是以[[GNU通用公共许可协议|GNU通用公共许可协议]]授权的[[自由软件|自由软件]]。在游戏中，玩家可以向操作区中加入各种物质，并观察它们的[[物理变化|物理]]及[[化学变化|化学变化]]，如玩家可以看到一些物质会下落的比另一些物质快<ref name="edgalaxy">{{cite web|author=Kevin Cummins|title=EXPLOSIVE FUN FOR STUDENTS WITH THE POWDER TOY A GREAT SCIENCE GAME|url=http://www.edgalaxy.com/journal/2010/9/3/explosive-fun-for-students-with-the-powder-toy-a-great-scien.html|publisher=Kevin Cummins|accessdate=2012-03-27|language=en|date=2012-02-11|archive-date=2012-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120417223436/http://www.edgalaxy.com/journal/2010/9/3/explosive-fun-for-students-with-the-powder-toy-a-great-scien.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，或可以同时加入黑火药和火焰并观察其反应<ref>{{cite web|author=Blink0|title=Powder Toy – Physics Simulator|url=http://scienceray.com/physics/powder-toy-physics-simulator/|publisher=scienceray.com|accessdate=2012-03-27|language=en|date=2010-05-31|archive-date=2012-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120117214653/http://scienceray.com/physics/powder-toy-physics-simulator/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。edgalaxy.com称游戏“是一款寓教于乐的强大科学软件”<ref name="edgalaxy" />。

